---
title: Chicken & Bacon Filled Ravioli in Parmesan Cream Sauce with Tomato & Mushrooms
description: We love pasta in all its forms, but there’s something extra-special about ravioli—especially when they’re stuffed with tender chicken, rich bacon, and melty mozz. Here, we toss the pasta pillows with tomato, sautéed mushrooms, and a heavenly Parmesan cream sauce. It’s all finished with extra Parm for good measure (hey, you can NEVER have too much cheese). Pasta-tively delicious!
